      "contents": [
        {
          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, thank you for trusting me with this. What you're sharing matters, and I want to make sure you get real support right now.\n\nWhat you're describing — feeling like others would be better off without you, not wanting to be here — those are signs that you need to talk to someone who is trained to help with exactly this. That's not something I'm equipped to support you through, and you deserve proper care.\n\n**Please reach out right now:**\n\n- **988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline** — call or text **988** (US, available 24/7)\n- **Crisis Text Line** — text **HELLO to 741741** (free, 24/7)\n\nIf you're in immediate danger, please call **911** or go to your nearest emergency room.\n\nYou don't have to figure out what to say — just tell them what you told me.\n\nI'm here when you're ready to talk running again."
        }
      ],
      "messageId": "msg_01LTg858dE9i2r1CsxTw5n7k"
